Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.54,0:31:12.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All my life I saw the goodness in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.06,0:31:18.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In the great and little~ things
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.55,0:31:24.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had strived to bring more everywhere I could
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.08,0:31:30.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like a flower in the~ spring
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.14,0:31:34.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yet I was so unconscious of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.40,0:31:37.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where ugliness could cling
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:41.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where such a pain might have fes~tered
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.89,0:31:46.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where I was need~ed to bring~~
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.36,0:31:50.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,True beauty inside
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.00,0:31:53.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not seeking glory
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.44,0:31:56.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Trying to justify
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:32:00.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had let decay~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.46,0:32:04.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So~ long
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.54,0:32:12.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,After years I found my village left in ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.03,0:32:17.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How I felt like such a~ fool
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.55,0:32:24.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That I'd let her steal all beauty that she could
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.00,0:32:31.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To create an empty~ jewel
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:34.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And what I found there upon the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.33,0:32:36.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In her abhorrent rule
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.59,0:32:41.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Was an old friend I cared about
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.81,0:32:47.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I had let her turn so cruel~~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.11,0:32:51.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All beauty outside
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.83,0:32:53.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Filling the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.22,0:32:57.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All an attempt to hide
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.64,0:33:07.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A curse born from an en~vious pride~~
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.58,0:33:10.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,How our village cried
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.29,0:33:13.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I should have seen
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.46,0:33:16.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The cause of this great divide
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.33,0:33:21.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now I had to face~ her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.49,0:33:25.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For beauty isn't ours a~lone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.33,0:33:30.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A thing to steal or hoard or own
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.24,0:33:35.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It is a light for all to~ see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.08,0:33:42.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A well of life to let flow~ free
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.72,0:34:10.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And in the end, when I held her there
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.99,0:34:13.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I knew I had to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.25,0:34:17.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Give up my beau~ty for everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.66,0:34:23.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And e~ven her too~~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.72,0:34:31.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,True beauty inside
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.40,0:34:34.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Shines on its own
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.76,0:34:37.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All vanity aside
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.47,0:34:47.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Frees those who let u~gliness hide~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.15,0:34:51.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All I could provide
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.82,0:34:53.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:57.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To help out your vil~lage too
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.82,0:35:01.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll do it to help~
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.32,0:35:05.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You~~